---
title: Chicken Schnitzel & Pesto Dressing with Garlic Roast Veggie Salad
description: This is no ordinary schnitzel; tonight's golden crumbed chicken dish features a medley of roasted veggies and a drizzle of creamy
pesto dressing for extra flair. With flavours like these, you won’t be missing your pub schnitty anytime soon!

